LANDING PAGE PROFESSIONAL PROMPT:
Design a comprehensive landing page for an AI-powered content intelligence platform that immediately communicates value and professionalism:

Visual Design:
- Hero section with bold, modern typography
- Clean, minimalist design with soft color palette
- High-contrast call-to-action buttons
- Responsive layout for desktop and mobile
- Subtle background gradient or geometric patterns

Key Section Components:
1. Hero Header
- Compelling headline highlighting AI content tools
- Subheadline explaining unique value proposition
- Free coin allocation prominently displayed
- "Get Started Free" primary button

2. Tool Feature Showcase
- Three-column layout showcasing core tools
- Professional icons for each tool
- Brief, impactful feature descriptions
- Hover interactions for each tool section

3. Social Proof Elements
- Logos of potential enterprise users
- Testimonial quotes
- Basic usage statistics
- Trust indicators (security, privacy commitments)

4. Authentication Options
- Clean login/signup form
- Social login buttons (Google, LinkedIn)
- Clear password reset link
- GDPR/privacy policy acknowledgment

Technical Considerations:
- Fast loading performance
- SEO-friendly structure
- Accessibility compliance
- Mobile-first design approach


